Another better approach is to use a Dynamic Structure like [ArrayList](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html). So here you need to have Array of ArrayList and then you can remove the element with [remove()](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html#remove(int)) method. In case if you want to update any element then you can use [set()](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html#set(int,%20E)) method.

